## Stack Tecnologico

| Componente | Version |
|------------|---------|
| Node.js | 22.x LTS |
| TypeScript | 5.5+ |
| Express | 4.21+ |
| PostgreSQL | 15+ |
| Drizzle ORM | 0.36+ |
| Vitest | 2.1+ |

## Prerequisitos

- Node.js >= 22.0.0
- npm >= 10.0.0
- Docker + Docker Compose
- PostgreSQL 15+ (local o via Docker)

## Inicio Rapido

```bash
# 1. Instalar dependencias
npm ci

# 2. Copiar variables de entorno
cp .env.sample .env

# 3. Levantar infraestructura local
docker compose up -d

# 4. Ejecutar en modo desarrollo
npm run dev
```

## Endpoints

| Metodo | Path | Descripcion |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `{{ context_path }}/api/v1/health` | Health check |
| GET | `{{ context_path }}/api-docs` | Swagger UI |
{% for module in modules %}
| GET | `{{ context_path }}/api/v1/{{ module.resource_path_resolved }}` | Listar {{ module.entity_name }} |
| POST | `{{ context_path }}/api/v1/{{ module.resource_path_resolved }}` | Crear {{ module.entity_name }} |
| GET | `{{ context_path }}/api/v1/{{ module.resource_path_resolved }}/:id` | Obtener {{ module.entity_name }} |
| PUT | `{{ context_path }}/api/v1/{{ module.resource_path_resolved }}/:id` | Actualizar {{ module.entity_name }} |
| DELETE | `{{ context_path }}/api/v1/{{ module.resource_path_resolved }}/:id` | Eliminar {{ module.entity_name }} |
{% endfor %}

## Scripts

| Comando | Descripcion |
|---------|-------------|
| `npm run dev` | Desarrollo con hot-reload (tsx watch) |
| `npm run build` | Compilar TypeScript |
| `npm start` | Ejecutar build compilado |
| `npm test` | Ejecutar tests |
| `npm run test:coverage` | Tests con reporte de coverage |
| `npm run lint` | Ejecutar ESLint |
| `npm run format` | Formatear con Prettier |

## Arquitectura

```
src/
├── app.ts              ← Configuracion Express
├── server.ts           ← Entry point
├── config/             ← Variables de entorno, DB, logger, security
├── commons/            ← DTOs transversales (ApiResponse, Pagination)
├── middleware/         ← Error handler, correlation-id, auth, validate
├── errors/             ← Errores custom de negocio
├── utils/              ← Sanitizacion, utilidades fecha
{% for module in modules %}
└── {{ module.module_name }}/           ← Dominio {{ module.entity_name }}
    ├── {{ module.module_name }}.controller.ts
    ├── {{ module.module_name }}.service.ts
    ├── {{ module.module_name }}.repository.ts
    ├── {{ module.module_name }}.schema.ts
    ├── dto/
    └── tests/
{% endfor %}
```

## Autenticacion

Estrategia: `{{ auth_strategy }}`

{% if auth_strategy == "oauth2-resource-server" %}
